message.content:
Kia ora! Ka whakamārama ahau i te āhua o te hokohoko māori i te mākete pūtea mā te whakapā mai ki te whare hoko pūtea, whakarongo mai ki te whakarongo ki taku whakamārama i roto i te reo Māori.

1. Whakapā ki te whare hoko pūtea:
   - Me tīmata e whakapā ki te whare hoko pūtea. Ka tono koe ki te whakapau kaha ki te kōwhiringa e whai ake nei.
   - Kati, whakapā ki te tauira o te whare hoko pūtea. Haere ki te whakapā, "Tēnā koe! Ka whai ahau i te anga whakamua ki te hoko mātou i ēnei putanga pūtea."
   - Whakapā mai ki te whare hoko pūtea i ngā whakararuraru, whakapau kaha, me ngā whakararuraru katoa.
   - Whakapā mai ki te whare hoko pūtea i ngā whakapau kaha, whakararuraru, me ngā take e pā ana ki te whakapau kaha ki te hokohoko pūtea.

2. Whakarongo ki te whakamārama:
   - Whakarongo mai ki te whakamārama a te tangata i te pūranga o ngā putanga pūtea e whai ake nei.
   - Whakarongo ki ngā whakararuraru, ngā whakapau kaha, me ngā raru katoa e whakapau kaha ana ki te whakapau kaha ki te hokohoko pūtea.
   - Whakarongo ki ngā whakapau kaha, ngā whakararuraru, me ngā take katoa e pā ana ki te whakapau kaha ki te hokohoko pūtea.

3. Whakautu ki ngā
